  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个支付核心系统的流程图。用户请求首先进入PaymentGateway，然后要经过身份认证，这个环节我想用AuthVault来单独表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，PaymentGateway作为入口，AuthVault做认证。认证完之后是回到同一个网关处理，还是进入下一个独立服务？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "认证通过后需要再回到PaymentGateway做一次路由判断，然后进入TransactionQueue做异步排队。最后由LedgerService完成记账。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以流程是：PaymentGateway → AuthVault → PaymentGateway → TransactionQueue → LedgerService。中间这个PaymentGateway出现两次，是同一个节点还是表示两个不同阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是同一个网关服务，但代表两次不同的处理。一次是接收请求，一次是认证后的路由转发。为了清晰，我在图里希望画成两个节点，但都标注为PaymentGateway。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把五个节点都创建出来：入口PaymentGateway、AuthVault、二次处理的PaymentGateway、TransactionQueue、以及最后的LedgerService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "连线关系确认一下：入口网关指向AuthVault，AuthVault指回网关，网关再指向TransactionQueue，最后队列指向LedgerService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "连线已完成。现在检查一遍：入口PaymentGateway到AuthVault，AuthVault到第二个PaymentGateway，再到TransactionQueue，最后到LedgerService。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "稍等，我刚才描述有误。AuthVault认证之后应该是直接连到TransactionQueue，不需要再经过一次PaymentGateway。我把中间那个节点理解错了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "那需要调整：去掉第二个PaymentGateway节点，让AuthVault直接连TransactionQueue？还是保留两个PaymentGateway但改变连线方式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "保留两个PaymentGateway，但连线改成：第一个PaymentGateway到AuthVault，AuthVault到第二个PaymentGateway，第二个PaymentGateway到TransactionQueue，TransactionQueue到LedgerService。这样更符合实际——网关始终负责入口和出口的控制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认最终结构：入口PaymentGateway → AuthVault → 二次PaymentGateway → TransactionQueue → LedgerService。四段连线，五个节点，其中PaymentGateway出现两次。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这就是我们要的支付核心流程。AuthVault独立出来做安全隔离，TransactionQueue做流量削峰，LedgerService保证最终一致性。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
